          },
          "reviewBody": "We have visited many play schools in and around thudiyalur. We felt that Chuvadu is the best play school. My daughter Ananya was studying PRE KG. The warmth and care from the staff especially Sofiya mam made my daughter feel at home . Play way learning, engaging activities and child-friendly environment have sparked my daughter's curiosity and love for learning.  Maintains excellent hygiene and safe environment. Weekly curriculum update. Constant touch with the parents. In fact my daughter even wants to go to school on holidays also which shows how she loves her time.Correspondent Preetha mam and Sampath sir are very friendly and approachable.\nStaffs, especially Vasanti Akka takes care of the kids very well. When my child was unwell, and Vasanti akka made sure she was comfortable, even letting her lie down on her lap for rest. It’s this kind of warmth and personal attention that makes all the difference. Affordable fees. Overall Chuvadu is the perfect school for my daughter's early learning journey.",
