          "reviewBody": "Earlier it was little millineum under the same management as of now . My kid did his playgroup and prekg . Earlier it was all fine and we were happy about management. In his pre kg one of co student put scratch marks on his face right below the eyes with safety pin and chart pins ( which were lying here n there inside) . When I noticed at he never accepted his friend did it and later after asking him for hours he confessed. We spoke to management very politely sharing all the images of the mark Askin these and to take care that this doesn't happen again. It again happened for the second time right below his eyes. The management was so rude that She yelled at us saying u cannot talk to parents asking about these and u cannot blame another kid ( not sure if it was some kinda politics ) for this he would have done on the way to home or at home . As we already planned not to continue there we never spoke or wrote about it . Parents please be careful and check if ur kids on Scratch marks of any right after school.\nOf course I remember bcz it was my kids first teachers hema and asrin who were excellent and aunties who groomed him . All I would wish to convey is the management was so rude while answering and denied our freedom of speech with other  parents.\n\nNo clarification was given but in turn u people cut the call yelling to us without any eithics and morals , another person from from management again called us asking apology .\n\nDint wanna make this this an issue but it's better that I drop a review so that it will help parents to be cautious .",
